{"tid":2206404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大深圳醫院擬與醫管局病歷互通 盧寵茂：會保障病人私隱","createTime":"2020-09-17T12:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T13:46:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"88b7728b811a5fbbdbc44bdf91020fe864365355","tid":2206404,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐全球大半年，不少港人因疫情滯留內地，部份有長期病患者未能回港取藥及覆診，政府日前已宣佈將委托港大深圳醫院，為長期居於廣東省的醫管局專科或普通科門診病人提供跟進診症服務。<span class=\"red\">香港大學深圳醫院院長盧寵茂期望，該院能在病人同意下，經「醫健通」電子健康紀錄系統，將病人在醫管局及深圳醫院的病歷互通，以確保醫療質素，並強調會保障病人私隱</span>。就港府日前宣佈，委託該院為長期居於廣東的醫管局病人覆診，盧則稱目前未有定案...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/7OPDPXMKFVC27GCKMO3O5ZX7BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2F7OPDPXMKFVC27GCKMO3O5ZX7BA%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=23bb8dbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2F7OPDPXMKFVC27GCKMO3O5ZX7BA%2F&h=e2ab00c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/7OPDPXMKFVC27GCKMO3O5ZX7BA/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6a4ef467beea3d3526a4a446cede57df528c9b","tid":2206404,"uid":192776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"439c3fd32f45219a813156bb0bd521db10aac15d","tid":2206404,"uid":47697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"自動送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2653015c3f311c53e5365194d1fcafc81d7fa8b","tid":2206404,"uid":271497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"揾鬼信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b0fcceafd5f9f3dbb75b199b941b3327fd9996","tid":2206404,"uid":41873,"like":2,"dislike":